{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "e-commerce-api-2026",
    "name": "E-Commerce API - Phase 1",
    "description": "Complete API collection for E-Commerce Backend System\n\nThis collection includes:\n- Authentication (Registration + Login with Strong Password)\n- Product browsing with filters (Public)\n- Shopping cart (Guest & Customer)\n- Checkout with stock reservation\n- Order management\n- Public order tracking (HTML view or JSON)\n- Email notifications (Gmail SMTP)\n- Admin operations\n\nPassword Requirements (Strong):\n- Minimum 8 characters\n- At least 1 uppercase, 1 lowercase, 1 digit, 1 special char\n\nOrder Status Flow: PENDING → CONFIRMED → PROCESSING → SHIPPED → DELIVERED\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register New Customer",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"customer_token\", jsonData.data.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"customer_id\", jsonData.data.user.id);",
                  "    console.log(\"✓ New customer registered and auto-logged in\");",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"newcustomer@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"NewCustomer@123\",\n  \"fullName\": \"New Test Customer\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Register new customer account with strong password validation.\n\nPassword Requirements:\n- Minimum 8 characters\n- At least 1 uppercase letter\n- At least 1 lowercase letter\n- At least 1 digit\n- At least 1 special character (@$!%*?&#^()_+=-{}[]|:;\"'<>,./)\n\nAuto-login after successful registration."
          },
          "response": []
        },
